    <h1>Branching Strategy</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col>
<col>
<col>
<col>
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Branch</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Use</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Pros</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Cons</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">master</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">current release</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>auto deploy to DEV env on merge</li>
<li>cannot checkin directly without PR</li>
<li>DEFAULT BRANCH</li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">may not match prod</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">develop</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">MESH recommendation for current release, but dev=
eloping against master is more efficient! MESH supports auto deploy from de=
velop?</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>cannot deploy non-master build SIT up</li>
<li>wont trigger fortify scan etc</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>release/MMM-YYYY-ERM</p><p>eg: release/May-20=
24-ERM&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">branched off master after successful release</td=
>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>feature/MMM-YYYY-ERM</p><p>eg: feature/May-20=
24-ERM&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">branched off master to work on vNext release whe=
n doing parallel development</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>progress development of next release before current release</li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>deploy only to swimlane (eg: w1c2)</li>
<li>need to sync often with master</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">feature/ART-11111</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Short-lived Feature branch. Once done raise PR t=
o master</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>developers can work in isolation without breaking anyone</li>
<li>deploy only to swimlane (eg: w1c2)</li>
</ul><p><br></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">bugfix/ART-11111</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Short-lived bugfix branch. Once done raise PR to=
 release branch</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">prodfix/ART-2222</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>For hotfixes in PROD, when master is ahead of=
 current release</p><p><span class=3D"plugin_pagetree_children_span plugin_=
pagetree_current"><a style=3D"" href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.=
au/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=3D1728257560&amp;src=3Dcontextnavpagetreemo=
de" rel=3D"nofollow">How to release to production from a non master branch =
(prodfix/* pattern)</a></span></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p><br></p>
